data.description: This is an 8-year-old home, perfect for a dream project. Priced at over $30,000 under the comps, this 4 bed, 3.5 bath Co is ripe for transformation. Inside you can install fresh floors, new carpet, and a splash of color to suit your taste. Outside, a quick makeover with a pressure wash, some sod in the backyard, and a little landscaping turn this into a haven. It's not just a house; it's your opportunity to reimagine living.    It has a bedroom with a private bathroom on the main floor and an oversized master suite with two more bedrooms upstairs.
